{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a fresh take on this action adventure of\u00a0 &quot;Spirit X Strike,&quot; featuring three intertwined combat systems: Instant Counter, Super Strike, and Spirit Mimicry. Players can swiftly switch between defense and attack, and experience an adrenaline-pumping combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538880/extras/mnggiflab-compressed-\u4e00\u95ea\u53cd\u51fb__1_.gif?t=1733729355\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique Action storing and release system to break the limits of COMBO potential!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chain together action sequences using the game\u2019s distinctive Spirit Mimicry. This system allows you to freely assemble moves and unleash them at the moment you desire. Even newcomers can easily execute stunning combos and air-juggle confirms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538880/extras/mnggiflab-compressed-\u7075\u62f3\u62df\u60012.gif?t=1733729355\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s Strike Time!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Break your opponents\u2019 defense with well-timed counters and quick pressure, then execute them with the finishing &quot;Super Strike&quot;. There are a lot of different \u201cSuper Strike\u201d finishers for different situations waiting for you to try out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538880/extras/mnggiflab-compressed-\u8d85\u7ea7\u51b2\u51fb_1.gif?t=1733729355\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survival in Post-Apocalyptic Wasteland</p><